    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209570/extras/1bbeee81b5e9b0d4c9d8257ae83843d2.poster.avif?t=1747600937\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209570/extras/1bbeee81b5e9b0d4c9d8257ae83843d2.webm?t=1747600937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209570/extras/1bbeee81b5e9b0d4c9d8257ae83843d2.mp4?t=1747600937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Prepare you starship and venture into the Cosmic Rifts, There you will find reincarnated starships infused by the power of the Rift Singularity. Fight your way to the centre of the Rift and close it to seal its fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209570/extras/24ccfd7f60acdb79eb4673741bc58a32.avif?t=1747600937\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209570/extras_big/24ccfd7f60acdb79eb4673741bc58a32.avif?t=1747600937 width=800 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Why should you start playing cosmos?</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful Voxel Art</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bullet Hell Enjoyers will rejoice</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rouge lite enjoyers will be at home </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25 Unique Bosses with 5 Tiers of difficaulty </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ Starships to collect, purchasable through In-game currency only </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 Interstellar <strong>Cosmic Rift</strong> maps with procedural space debris</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collection log with all your important stats and rewards gained while playing </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compendium that keeps track of everything you have fought, killed and collected!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Missions and Challenges for co-pliots wanting to test themselves in the rifts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic OST produced by DEFCAT</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-Game Rating system, with Rating emotes for those who have proven worthly</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209570/extras/0a33206407524c538b5dda0df8931468.avif?t=1747600937\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209570/extras_big/0a33206407524c538b5dda0df8931468.avif?t=1747600937 width=800 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Augment your starship with upgrades obtained by leveling up, completing challenges set by your fellow co-pilots and buying them from the Black Market.  <br> <br>Augments can be swapped out before entering a rift allowing you to create any number of cool and unique builds to close the harder and harder rifts!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209570/extras/ff7e9f1046edf918ec87f12208785458.avif?t=1747600937\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209570/extras_big/ff7e9f1046edf918ec87f12208785458.avif?t=1747600937 width=800 height=86 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Artifacts are the embodiedment of power harvested from the etherial creatures known as Cosmic Echos! Artifacts change, warp and modify your starship. There are over <strong>100</strong> Unique Artifacts, Curses and Boons to collect, here are some of them in action!<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209570/extras/495f07d93403d71b9cc1835eec4eaada.poster.avif?t=1747600937\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209570/extras/495f07d93403d71b9cc1835eec4eaada.webm?t=1747600937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209570/extras/495f07d93403d71b9cc1835eec4eaada.mp4?t=1747600937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEV PROMISE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Monthly Updates</strong> - I'm commited to update this game with new content, starships, bosses, artifacts and bugfixes since its release in 2018 and have been updating it ever since!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
